WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 39]

02:55.020 --> 02:57.250
The former Lady Fu Ling was spirited and resolute,

02:57.280 --> 02:58.730
with swift and ruthless judgment.

02:58.750 --> 02:59.750
Although you are holding a sharp blade,

02:59.800 --> 03:01.660
there’s no opportunity to wield it.

03:01.680 --> 03:03.340
What a pity.

03:03.750 --> 03:05.840
Why don't I give you a chance?

03:06.260 --> 03:07.510
What do you want?

03:13.500 --> 03:14.750
I've said that

03:14.990 --> 03:17.680
once I've returned, I shall reign supreme over the world.

03:17.700 --> 03:20.420
Although the Eastern Continent's Eternals and demons are weak,

03:20.450 --> 03:22.230
a good number of them collectively

03:23.090 --> 03:25.329
makes for a decent supplement.

03:25.380 --> 03:27.060
As long as you obey

03:27.100 --> 03:29.260
and capture Eternals and demons for me,

03:29.290 --> 03:31.040
you are allowed to enter and exit

03:31.910 --> 03:33.500
Cold Spring Palace freely.

03:36.820 --> 03:38.940
After all,

03:38.970 --> 03:40.650
you used to do this sort of thing all the time,

03:40.670 --> 03:41.620
didn’t you?

03:46.640 --> 03:48.190
No way.

03:52.850 --> 03:55.280
What if Chong Zhao's life is at stake?

03:55.310 --> 03:57.260
Let's see how you choose.

04:06.860 --> 04:07.850
Chong Zhao!

04:08.650 --> 04:09.700
Xi.

04:13.010 --> 04:13.900
Xi.

04:14.510 --> 04:15.480
Chong Zhao.

04:16.570 --> 04:17.740
You are still here.

04:18.680 --> 04:20.019
You really are still here.

04:20.209 --> 04:22.190
There’s still so much we haven’t accomplished yet.

04:23.080 --> 04:24.810
I know you're waiting for me.

04:25.470 --> 04:27.110
I won't disappear so easily.

04:27.130 --> 04:28.660
How sincere

04:28.680 --> 04:29.870
and touching.

04:29.900 --> 04:31.230
Actually, the existence of you two

04:31.260 --> 04:32.480
is not something

04:32.800 --> 04:34.330
I find entirely unacceptable.

04:38.570 --> 04:39.740
Chong Zhao.

04:40.050 --> 04:41.380
Persuade her well.

04:41.409 --> 04:42.850
Instead of resisting,

04:42.870 --> 04:44.460
why not obey me?

04:44.490 --> 04:46.780
That's the only wise choice.

04:49.350 --> 04:50.350
Xi.

04:51.300 --> 04:52.550
You were forced to be a demon for ten years

04:52.580 --> 04:53.810
and suffered for ten years.

04:53.840 --> 04:55.290
You finally escaped Cold Spring Palace

04:55.310 --> 04:56.650
to become Bai Xi again.

04:56.670 --> 04:58.750
You must not go back to your old ways.

04:58.790 --> 05:00.350
The righteousness of the world

05:00.380 --> 05:03.050
and your future is always more important than my life.

05:03.070 --> 05:04.320
Don't you ever feel threatened by him.

05:04.340 --> 05:06.370
That's not what I want to hear.

05:10.070 --> 05:11.070
Zhao!

05:12.450 --> 05:13.450
Zhao!

05:14.710 --> 05:15.790
Xi.

05:16.500 --> 05:17.610
Remember,

05:17.640 --> 05:19.610
regardless of how Mo Li treats me,

05:19.630 --> 05:21.480
even if he kills me,

05:21.610 --> 05:24.040
you mustn't give in to him.

05:30.350 --> 05:32.350
How stubborn.

05:34.010 --> 05:36.070
I really don't understand

05:36.320 --> 05:37.990
why you would fall for

05:38.010 --> 05:39.650
such a boring and stubborn person.

05:40.520 --> 05:42.100
You will

05:42.409 --> 05:44.420
never understand his loyalty!

05:44.440 --> 05:46.000
Your so-called morality

05:46.020 --> 05:48.810
is the most hypocritical and ridiculous in my eyes.

05:50.320 --> 05:51.610
I may have given you a chance,

05:51.640 --> 05:54.030
but that doesn't mean you are irreplaceable.

05:54.050 --> 05:55.540
Since you don't appreciate it,

05:55.570 --> 05:57.490
you can just stand by and watch

05:57.510 --> 06:00.390
how the Eternals and demons grovel at my feet,

06:00.420 --> 06:01.900
begging for mercy.

06:07.680 --> 06:09.190
Xiu Yan once said

06:09.220 --> 06:10.040
he could feel that

06:10.060 --> 06:12.180
the Xing Yue Divine Bow is right above the Eastern Continent.

06:12.210 --> 06:13.770
But no matter how I summon it,

06:13.790 --> 06:15.640
the Divine Bow wouldn't appear.

06:15.660 --> 06:18.700
The Contemplation Stone and the Outlander King's Sword also had no reaction to it.

06:18.730 --> 06:21.100
The Contemplation Stone and the Sword acknowledged you as its master

06:21.120 --> 06:22.160
because they sensed that

06:22.190 --> 06:23.710
you have Xing Yue's Divine Mantle,

06:23.740 --> 06:25.380
but the Xing Yue Bow remained completely silent.

06:26.080 --> 06:26.960
Unless...

06:27.620 --> 06:29.290
Unless it's not yet awakened

06:29.310 --> 06:30.630
and doesn't know it's a Divine Bow.

06:31.000 --> 06:33.640
Back then, the Xing Yue Divine Bow could defy Xing Yue's own wishes

06:33.659 --> 06:34.980
and shot Jing Yuan down.

06:35.010 --> 06:37.250
This means it has its own consciousness.

06:37.270 --> 06:38.740
It's different from other divine objects.

06:42.420 --> 06:43.490
Bad news.

06:44.070 --> 06:46.020
Mo Li launched a sudden attack on various demon clans and Eternal sects.

06:46.050 --> 06:47.490
Many Eternals and demons have nowhere to go.

06:47.510 --> 06:49.000
They've all fled to the Polar Region for refuge.

06:49.030 --> 06:50.150
Mo Li has gathered several demon warriors

06:50.170 --> 06:51.409
to attack the Polar Region.

06:54.140 --> 06:56.110
The Polar Region's terrain is vast and complex.

06:56.130 --> 06:58.050
It's certainly possible to take in the Eternals and demons seeking refuge.

06:58.080 --> 06:59.600
I believe the demon warriors of Bright Moon Palace

06:59.620 --> 07:00.660
are not afraid of a battle.

07:00.690 --> 07:01.800
But here in the Polar Region,

07:01.830 --> 07:03.980
there are also many little demons that you saved.

07:04.010 --> 07:05.240
If Mo Li attacks,

07:05.260 --> 07:06.670
they won't be able to withstand it.

07:06.700 --> 07:08.970
On the day we established this palace in the Polar Region,

07:08.990 --> 07:11.540
I made it clear that no one would be allowed to encroach on my territory.

07:12.270 --> 07:13.630
What are you trying to do?

07:14.950 --> 07:17.110
Jing Yuan left all of his divine power to me.

07:17.320 --> 07:19.480
I can summon the Purple Moon above the Polar Region

07:19.510 --> 07:21.820
and protect the entire Polar Region with my primal power.

07:21.910 --> 07:23.750
Although the primal power of the Demon Lord is strong,

07:23.770 --> 07:25.900
the Polar Region spans hundreds of thousands of miles of land.

07:25.930 --> 07:27.970
If you form a barrier with your divine power,

07:27.990 --> 07:29.740
it will inevitably consume your power continuously.

07:29.760 --> 07:30.670
Master.

07:30.690 --> 07:32.280
You're draining yourself.

07:33.500 --> 07:35.250
Anyone who comes to the Polar Region,

07:35.280 --> 07:36.600
whether an Eternal or a demon,

07:36.620 --> 07:38.500
is entrusting their life to me.

07:39.140 --> 07:40.710
I will protect them all.

07:41.140 --> 07:42.020
Master!

07:45.480 --> 07:46.640
Aren't you going to stop him?

07:47.060 --> 07:48.880
If he isn't going to resolve matters this way,

07:48.900 --> 07:51.020
he wouldn’t be the Master of Bright Moon Palace

07:51.080 --> 07:52.820
or the Fan Yue I know.

07:53.590 --> 07:55.250
He has endured too much suffering

07:55.280 --> 07:56.640
and faced too many hardships in the past.

07:56.659 --> 07:58.220
That's why he wants to stand in front of others

07:58.250 --> 07:59.690
and shield those who are also suffering.

08:00.980 --> 08:02.720
This is his choice.

08:02.900 --> 08:05.400
I agree and I won't stop him.

08:05.940 --> 08:07.450
As for my choice...

08:07.480 --> 08:08.920
I've already told you,

08:09.710 --> 08:11.480
We shall fight side by side,

08:11.510 --> 08:13.060
sharing both life and death.

09:10.370 --> 09:11.410
Purple Moon!

09:11.430 --> 09:13.840
-It's the Purple Moon!
-It's the Purple Moon!

09:14.090 --> 09:15.520
It's the Purple Moon! Look!

09:18.030 --> 09:18.990
Purple Moon!

09:25.930 --> 09:28.450
It's the Demon Lord who is using the Purple Lunar Power to form a barrier

09:28.860 --> 09:30.820
in order to block Mo Li's attack.

09:30.850 --> 09:33.330
I didn't expect that us Eternals have to escape to the Polar Region

09:33.350 --> 09:34.300
and receive protection from Fan Yue

09:34.330 --> 09:35.730
in order to survive.

09:46.820 --> 09:47.670
Fan Yue.

09:49.960 --> 09:50.960
I'm fine.

09:51.370 --> 09:53.140
Previously, Eternals and demons all believed that

09:53.160 --> 09:55.230
the Master of Bright Moon was ruthless by nature.

09:55.260 --> 09:56.830
Now, they will all know that

09:56.850 --> 09:59.090
you are the most merciful one.

09:59.120 --> 10:00.790
It doesn't matter whether they know or not.

10:01.760 --> 10:03.000
What matters is

10:03.020 --> 10:04.870
no matter what happens next,

10:04.900 --> 10:06.900
I mustn't allow Mo Li's wild ambitions succeed.

10:07.560 --> 10:08.910
60,000 years ago,

10:08.940 --> 10:10.570
Mo Li destroyed the Divine Region.

10:10.600 --> 10:11.880
60,000 years later,

10:11.900 --> 10:13.750
I won't let him destroy the Eastern Continent again.

10:18.290 --> 10:20.240
It was exactly this Purple Moon that

10:20.260 --> 10:21.870
gave me immense hope back then.

10:23.340 --> 10:25.670
It's the same this time.

10:37.860 --> 10:39.410
The appearance of the Purple Moon

10:39.440 --> 10:40.800
will protect the Eternals and demons.

10:40.820 --> 10:41.660
Mo Li,

10:42.330 --> 10:43.870
you can't win after all.

10:43.890 --> 10:46.080
Do you really think that the Purple Moon's protection of the Polar Region

10:46.150 --> 10:48.700
will safeguard those Eternals and demons for a lifetime?

10:48.730 --> 10:50.430
No one can stop me

10:50.460 --> 10:52.070
from doing what I want.

10:52.730 --> 10:54.900
Shuo and Fan Yue won't sit back and do nothing.

10:54.930 --> 10:57.080
I'm sure they'll find a way to restrain you.

10:58.060 --> 10:58.990
Really?

11:00.630 --> 11:03.230
I'm afraid the Human Race can't wait till then.

11:04.150 --> 11:05.350
What do you mean?

11:05.490 --> 11:06.870
The humans are unaware of the Eternals, the demons,

11:06.910 --> 11:08.210
or the Polar Region,

11:08.290 --> 11:10.230
nor do they know about the impending catastrophe in the world.

11:10.250 --> 11:11.630
They're still at the same place,

11:11.630 --> 11:12.890
living their peaceful lives.

11:12.910 --> 11:15.400
The Purple Moon can barely safeguard the Polar Region as it is.

11:15.430 --> 11:17.690
How can it protect the entire Human Race?

11:17.710 --> 11:18.820
You're...

11:19.020 --> 11:20.760
You're actually planning to target the Human Race?

11:20.790 --> 11:22.310
You're at least an ancient god.

11:22.330 --> 11:23.380
How could you be this despicable?

11:29.820 --> 11:31.060
In my eyes,

11:31.420 --> 11:33.350
there is only success or failure.

11:33.490 --> 11:35.340
There's no such thing as benevolence or otherwise.

11:38.990 --> 11:40.030
Tomorrow,

11:40.900 --> 11:43.870
I'll put on a good show for you.

12:39.950 --> 12:41.600
Are you satisfied

12:42.270 --> 12:43.980
with this show?

12:48.980 --> 12:50.730
You want to use human blood

12:50.750 --> 12:52.410
to break the Purple Lunar Barrier?

12:54.340 --> 12:55.910
The Purple Moon's divine power is extremely yang,

12:55.930 --> 12:57.670
while human blood is extremely yin.

12:57.690 --> 12:59.120
Yin and yang neutralizes each other,

13:00.340 --> 13:01.580
so why not?

13:07.860 --> 13:09.750
Kill me if you dare!

13:13.330 --> 13:15.570
Killing you would be too easy.

13:15.590 --> 13:17.240
It's only fun if I torture you.

13:17.270 --> 13:18.860
Offering the blood of thousands

13:18.880 --> 13:20.480
will surely incur heaven's wrath

13:20.780 --> 13:22.110
Heaven's wrath?

13:23.210 --> 13:25.510
If the Heaven is capable of killing me,

13:25.540 --> 13:28.300
I would have died 60,000 years ago.

13:28.770 --> 13:30.520
Heaven has set a rule that only a Supreme Deity

13:30.540 --> 13:32.750
can completely kill another Supreme Deity.

13:32.780 --> 13:35.270
Even the Heaven has to follow its own rules.

13:39.370 --> 13:40.280
Sacrifice?

14:03.870 --> 14:05.950
Look at the scenery.

14:06.790 --> 14:08.630
Blood staining the Polar Region.

14:09.390 --> 14:11.490
How spectacular!

14:29.090 --> 14:30.740
You'll face retribution.

14:31.440 --> 14:33.240
You'll definitely face retribution!

14:33.270 --> 14:34.250
Shut up!

14:36.740 --> 14:38.530
I think I am already hearing

14:38.930 --> 14:41.900
the blood currents climbing over the Purple Lunar Barrier.

14:47.490 --> 14:48.730
Very soon...

14:57.460 --> 14:58.220
Master.

14:58.250 --> 15:00.340
All the Eternals and demons seeking refuge have been taken care of.

15:00.360 --> 15:01.310
In the face of a powerful enemy,

15:01.340 --> 15:03.310
both sides have set aside their past prejudices

15:03.330 --> 15:04.520
and are living in peace.

15:09.390 --> 15:10.330
Master.

15:10.470 --> 15:11.470
What's wrong?

15:11.660 --> 15:12.870
Are you not feeling well?

15:13.800 --> 15:15.230
-Master!
-Fan Yue!

15:22.420 --> 15:23.310
What's going on?

15:30.280 --> 15:31.580
Human blood sacrifice?

15:32.380 --> 15:34.210
The Purple Lunar Barrier has been broken.

15:46.930 --> 15:47.920
Xi!

15:48.570 --> 15:49.770
Shuo, I'm fine.

15:54.280 --> 15:56.190
You're finally here.

15:56.670 --> 15:59.180
Chong Zhao would never commit such a heinous act as a human blood sacrifice.

15:59.210 --> 16:00.970
You are nothing like him.

16:00.990 --> 16:02.960
How could a weak and incompetent Chong Zhao

16:02.990 --> 16:04.710
ever compare to me?

16:06.380 --> 16:09.320
The human blood broke the Purple Lunar Barrier so quickly.

16:09.350 --> 16:11.500
It seems that you are no longer Jing Yuan.

16:11.530 --> 16:13.410
Whether I'm Fan Yue or Jing Yuan,

16:14.000 --> 16:15.780
I won't let you succeed.

16:17.410 --> 16:18.880
The indiscriminate killing of

16:18.900 --> 16:20.320
innocent humans is utterly inhumane.

16:20.350 --> 16:21.380
Mo Li.

16:21.400 --> 16:23.090
You don't deserve to be a deity.

16:23.110 --> 16:24.990
That's not up to you to decide.

16:25.960 --> 16:27.150
You all...

16:27.870 --> 16:29.950
can't stop me from achieving my grand plan.

16:49.580 --> 16:51.240
You've clearly overestimated your abilities.

17:08.780 --> 17:10.930
You only have Xing Yue's Divine Mantle.

17:10.950 --> 17:13.220
Now without the power of the Contemplation Stone,

17:13.240 --> 17:14.349
you're nothing but an ant

17:14.369 --> 17:16.119
in my eyes.

17:46.330 --> 17:48.060
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

17:48.310 --> 17:50.530
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

17:50.590 --> 17:52.150
♫My love brought tears♫

17:52.470 --> 17:54.350
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

17:54.650 --> 17:56.400
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

17:56.810 --> 17:57.810
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

17:58.230 --> 18:00.000
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

18:00.430 --> 18:02.160
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

18:02.680 --> 18:04.160
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

18:04.520 --> 18:06.250
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

18:06.520 --> 18:08.490
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

18:08.830 --> 18:10.520
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

18:10.840 --> 18:12.350
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

18:12.900 --> 18:14.750
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

18:15.040 --> 18:16.700
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

18:16.900 --> 18:19.150
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

18:55.150 --> 18:56.420
Where am I?

18:59.240 --> 19:00.540
This is the Unbridled Pavilion.

19:01.250 --> 19:03.010
Fan Yue took us back to Ning'an City.

19:04.210 --> 19:05.940
Ning'an City?

19:07.360 --> 19:09.360
I'm finally back.

19:09.800 --> 19:11.430
Don't talk.

19:11.640 --> 19:13.000
Let me give you some energy.

19:15.080 --> 19:17.450
Shuo, don't cry.

19:17.470 --> 19:18.990
In this lifetime,

19:19.030 --> 19:20.670
it has been my greatest fortune

19:20.710 --> 19:22.910
to be able to reunite with you.

19:23.800 --> 19:25.310
But from now on,

19:26.920 --> 19:29.070
I can't protect you any longer.

19:30.820 --> 19:33.680
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

19:34.520 --> 19:37.060
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

19:36.080 --> 19:37.290
No.

19:37.880 --> 19:41.640
♫I remember that word of concern♫

19:38.460 --> 19:40.390
We've only just reunited.

19:41.320 --> 19:43.230
Didn't we agree to

19:42.270 --> 19:45.510
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

19:43.250 --> 19:45.660
overcome difficulties

19:45.690 --> 19:47.780
and start over together?

19:46.010 --> 19:48.820
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

19:49.560 --> 19:51.710
Don't leave me, will you?

19:49.580 --> 19:52.970
♫It dried in the wind♫

19:52.040 --> 19:54.820
I don't want you to leave you either, Shuo.

19:53.650 --> 19:55.300
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

19:55.830 --> 19:59.440
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

19:56.090 --> 19:58.020
But in this lifetime of mine,

19:58.060 --> 20:00.700
I've done too much wrong.

20:00.480 --> 20:03.680
♫That year, that year♫

20:00.720 --> 20:02.580
I have to make up for it somehow.

20:02.850 --> 20:05.020
The ten years spent in Cold Spring Palace

20:04.260 --> 20:07.470
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

20:08.090 --> 20:11.600
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

20:08.180 --> 20:10.370
were like shackles

20:11.180 --> 20:13.000
that held me captive.

20:12.230 --> 20:14.720
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

20:14.020 --> 20:15.460
Maybe this way,

20:15.680 --> 20:19.000
♫That year, that year♫

20:16.910 --> 20:19.110
I can be truly free.

20:19.440 --> 20:22.620
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

20:20.520 --> 20:21.570
Shuo.

20:22.550 --> 20:24.040
Don't be sad.

20:23.430 --> 20:26.560
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

20:25.390 --> 20:26.540
Remember.

20:27.680 --> 20:30.180
The stars shine brightly

20:27.710 --> 20:30.440
♫Layer after layer♫

20:30.400 --> 20:32.810
as the moon emerges from the clouds.

20:32.830 --> 20:34.100
I'm like the morning light,

20:34.130 --> 20:35.660
while you are like the stars.

20:34.440 --> 20:37.960
♫That year, that year♫

20:35.760 --> 20:37.230
The stars shine brightly

20:37.260 --> 20:38.990
as the moon emerges from the clouds.

20:38.390 --> 20:41.310
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

20:39.810 --> 20:41.440
You must always...

20:42.210 --> 20:45.610
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

20:43.120 --> 20:44.770
always...

20:45.470 --> 20:48.410
be the invincible Bai Shuo.

20:46.500 --> 20:49.220
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

20:50.030 --> 20:53.370
♫That year, that year♫

20:52.910 --> 20:54.680
I'm not leaving.

20:53.860 --> 20:57.050
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

20:55.260 --> 20:56.980
I'm just tired,

20:57.850 --> 21:01.000
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

20:58.330 --> 21:00.120
and I want to go home.

21:02.040 --> 21:04.550
♫Layer after layer♫

21:05.470 --> 21:09.070
♫Another year passed♫

21:10.490 --> 21:12.860
Ning'an City...

21:12.220 --> 21:16.420
♫Another year passed♫

21:14.070 --> 21:15.630
The Governor's Mansion...

21:16.540 --> 21:18.180
I think...

21:19.090 --> 21:21.150
I see Father.

21:48.080 --> 21:50.250
Father, when can we eat?

21:51.070 --> 21:52.470
I'm starving.

21:52.530 --> 21:53.210
Just wait.

21:59.780 --> 22:02.150
Xi, where have you been?

22:02.180 --> 22:03.360
Don't try to sneak a bite.

22:04.160 --> 22:05.450
Why are you home only now?

22:05.470 --> 22:07.310
Quick, come and have some dumplings.

22:07.340 --> 22:08.930
That's right, Xi.

22:08.950 --> 22:10.910
The dumplings are going to get cold if you don't eat.

22:10.940 --> 22:12.500
Hurry up.

22:13.760 --> 22:14.570
Hurry.

22:14.780 --> 22:16.220
-Come on. Have a seat.
-Here.

22:17.010 --> 22:18.200
-If you don't come back,
-Eat it while it’s hot.

22:18.220 --> 22:19.540
Father wouldn't even let me eat.

22:26.640 --> 22:27.670
Our dear Father

22:27.720 --> 22:28.950
might not be the best with other dishes,

22:28.970 --> 22:30.410
but these dumplings are at least decent.

22:30.440 --> 22:31.440
Decent?

22:31.460 --> 22:32.860
If it's just decent, then don't eat.

22:32.890 --> 22:34.140
Give it to Xi.

22:34.170 --> 22:35.170
Here.

22:35.940 --> 22:36.690
Xi,

22:37.830 --> 22:39.200
why aren't you eating?

22:39.590 --> 22:40.940
Eat the dumplings while it's hot.

22:40.960 --> 22:42.200
Eat your fill.

22:42.560 --> 22:43.320
That's right.

22:49.530 --> 22:50.250
Father.

22:51.920 --> 22:52.640
What's wrong?

22:54.990 --> 22:57.590
♫The last moonlight♫

22:57.730 --> 22:58.780
It's nothing.

22:58.380 --> 23:02.130
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

22:59.290 --> 23:02.800
I just haven't seen you for a long time,

23:03.170 --> 23:05.800
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

23:03.530 --> 23:04.810
so I wanted to call you.

23:06.490 --> 23:10.500
♫In this life, at this time♫

23:07.660 --> 23:08.830
It's my fault.

23:09.070 --> 23:11.140
I'm always busy with city's affairs,

23:10.840 --> 23:14.310
♫I dare not look back♫

23:11.170 --> 23:12.580
and I seldom spend time with you two.

23:13.380 --> 23:14.790
Please don't blame me.

23:15.090 --> 23:18.450
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

23:16.070 --> 23:17.750
I don't blame you.

23:17.810 --> 23:19.520
Why would I blame you?

23:19.490 --> 23:22.540
♫On your path?♫

23:20.190 --> 23:21.810
It's all my fault.

23:22.980 --> 23:24.810
I've let you down.

23:23.370 --> 23:26.410
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

23:24.830 --> 23:26.070
I don't...

23:26.100 --> 23:27.030
No, don't.

23:26.940 --> 23:30.490
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

23:27.370 --> 23:28.740
Xi, what's wrong?

23:29.720 --> 23:30.670
You...

23:30.780 --> 23:32.570
You haven't even had a bite of my dumplings,

23:31.060 --> 23:32.920
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

23:32.600 --> 23:34.230
and you are already crying just by the looks of it?

23:33.570 --> 23:34.580
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

23:35.160 --> 23:38.920
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

23:39.400 --> 23:41.160
You're even crying your eyes out.

23:39.720 --> 23:43.430
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

23:42.930 --> 23:45.610
I was just thinking about some...

23:43.700 --> 23:46.690
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

23:46.750 --> 23:48.650
some things I did before that hurt you.

23:47.220 --> 23:49.370
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

23:49.940 --> 23:51.270
♫Time after time♫

23:50.670 --> 23:52.230
Since it's all in the past,

23:52.030 --> 23:59.120
♫Oh, melancholy♫

23:52.260 --> 23:53.740
then just let it go.

23:53.760 --> 23:55.290
Have you forgotten what I've told you?

23:55.810 --> 23:57.160
In our Bai family,

23:57.190 --> 23:59.890
we don't stay angry overnight, and we don't hold grudges.

24:01.110 --> 24:03.590
As a family, there's no need to apologize to each other.

24:03.620 --> 24:05.120
-Right?
-Yeah.

24:07.940 --> 24:09.660
Alright, stop crying.

24:13.270 --> 24:14.170
Father.

24:14.720 --> 24:16.110
Xi is back.

24:16.760 --> 24:19.110
Xi will never leave you again.

24:19.130 --> 24:20.280
Never.

24:21.090 --> 24:22.090
All right.

24:22.930 --> 24:24.130
Yes, you won't leave.

24:24.150 --> 24:25.800
Since you've cried,

24:25.830 --> 24:28.210
then just forget all the unhappy memories.

24:28.540 --> 24:30.340
Hurry, try my dumplings.

24:30.370 --> 24:31.920
Let's see if it's just decent.

24:32.680 --> 24:34.940
Here, I'll get you another one.

24:37.190 --> 24:38.120
Hurry.

24:44.820 --> 24:45.970
How is it?

24:47.940 --> 24:49.240
It's delicious.

24:49.270 --> 24:50.270
Did you hear that?

24:50.290 --> 24:52.240
It's delicious, not just decent.

24:52.590 --> 24:54.150
If it's delicious, have some more.

25:32.350 --> 25:33.630
Shuo.

25:35.620 --> 25:37.370
If there's a next life,

25:37.980 --> 25:39.610
let's stay together

25:41.550 --> 25:43.350
as a family,

25:44.780 --> 25:46.050
shall we?

25:55.340 --> 26:00.300
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

26:03.460 --> 26:09.090
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

26:11.750 --> 26:19.180
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

26:20.100 --> 26:25.150
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

26:36.220 --> 26:39.650
♫Across thousands of miles♫

26:44.620 --> 26:49.100
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

26:52.110 --> 26:59.130
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

27:00.020 --> 27:05.250
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

27:02.700 --> 27:04.190
It's the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

27:04.770 --> 27:06.050
Bai Xi...

27:06.330 --> 27:08.410
is the bow spirit of Xing Yue Divine Bow?

27:35.270 --> 27:37.040
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

27:37.320 --> 27:39.470
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

27:39.530 --> 27:41.240
♫My love brought tears♫

27:41.540 --> 27:43.290
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

27:43.710 --> 27:45.540
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

27:45.750 --> 27:47.170
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

27:47.380 --> 27:49.000
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

27:49.370 --> 27:51.350
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

27:51.710 --> 27:53.160
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

27:53.430 --> 27:55.190
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

27:55.460 --> 27:57.570
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

27:57.850 --> 27:59.460
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

27:59.780 --> 28:01.330
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

28:01.840 --> 28:03.850
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

28:04.140 --> 28:05.430
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

28:05.840 --> 28:08.760
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

28:53.310 --> 28:55.910
Why does my heart ache?

29:08.130 --> 29:08.990
No.

29:09.970 --> 29:11.630
I am not one to feel any heartache

29:11.660 --> 29:13.160
nor shed any tears.

29:14.340 --> 29:15.770
Chong Zhao.

29:15.790 --> 29:17.090
It must be you!

29:24.500 --> 29:26.270
You're indeed behind this.

29:26.290 --> 29:27.570
Mo Li.

29:27.600 --> 29:29.410
I'll kill you!

29:35.040 --> 29:36.310
Do you really think

29:37.390 --> 29:39.120
you're capable of hurting me?

29:39.860 --> 29:41.850
Why did you kill her?

29:42.050 --> 29:44.170
I had spared her life,

29:44.300 --> 29:46.180
but she kept going against me

29:46.210 --> 29:47.420
and was courting her own demise.

29:48.120 --> 29:49.490
Chong Zhao.

29:49.520 --> 29:50.700
Leaving you with your divine consciousness

29:50.720 --> 29:52.520
is already a major grace from me.

29:52.550 --> 29:54.220
It's best if you remain obediently

29:54.240 --> 29:56.160
in the depths of this sea of consciousness.

29:56.190 --> 29:58.840
If you dare to disturb me again,

29:58.860 --> 30:00.490
I have no qualms of personally destroying

30:00.520 --> 30:01.970
your last sliver of divine consciousness.

30:01.990 --> 30:04.590
If you dare to destroy it, why haven't you done it yet?

30:04.610 --> 30:06.780
As long as my divine consciousness is gone,

30:06.810 --> 30:08.490
you will also be severely hurt.

30:09.600 --> 30:11.060
If you don't destroy it,

30:11.110 --> 30:12.350
I will.

30:20.840 --> 30:22.060
Let go of me!

30:22.420 --> 30:24.510
Destroying your own divine consciousness?

30:25.460 --> 30:27.410
Dream on!

30:31.160 --> 30:32.560
Why are you laughing?

30:32.740 --> 30:35.060
I’m laughing because you’re pathetic.

30:35.090 --> 30:36.810
You call yourself a deity,

30:36.830 --> 30:39.110
but you have no idea what love is,

30:39.140 --> 30:41.130
and no one loves you.

30:41.160 --> 30:43.470
You keep saying you want to marry Xing Yue,

30:43.490 --> 30:45.600
but that's only because you can't get her

30:45.630 --> 30:47.990
and are trying to claim her through bloodshed.

30:48.040 --> 30:49.560
But let me tell you,

30:49.590 --> 30:50.880
you're wrong.

30:50.920 --> 30:53.660
Love in this world can never come from possession.

31:00.670 --> 31:01.890
You insignificant fools

31:01.920 --> 31:03.700
are on the verge of death,

31:04.110 --> 31:06.710
yet you dare speak of love in front of me.

31:08.520 --> 31:09.880
How ridiculous.

31:20.620 --> 31:21.520
Chong Zhao.

31:31.150 --> 31:32.260
Xi!

31:36.090 --> 31:37.290
Xi.

31:44.070 --> 31:45.130
Xi!

31:52.660 --> 31:58.870
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

31:55.010 --> 31:55.910
Xi.

32:00.300 --> 32:05.920
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

32:01.050 --> 32:02.690
I've let you down.

32:04.360 --> 32:06.600
I failed to protect you.

32:06.620 --> 32:07.820
I'm sorry.

32:07.370 --> 32:09.870
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

32:11.230 --> 32:14.410
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

32:12.380 --> 32:13.900
I'm sorry.

32:13.920 --> 32:15.360
Chong Zhao.

32:14.990 --> 32:20.760
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

32:15.390 --> 32:16.750
Don't cry, will you?

32:17.480 --> 32:20.310
All of this is my personal choice.

32:20.930 --> 32:22.610
The Divine Bow is emotionless.

32:22.180 --> 32:28.800
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

32:22.640 --> 32:24.440
Even if I live for thousands of years,

32:24.460 --> 32:26.370
I will never comprehend the true meaning of the world.

32:26.920 --> 32:28.710
Having met you in this lifetime,

32:28.840 --> 32:30.640
I already have no regrets.

32:29.570 --> 32:35.940
♫All the answers are already explained♫

32:32.340 --> 32:33.750
Chong Zhao.

32:34.010 --> 32:35.700
If there's a next life,

32:36.360 --> 32:39.010
let's live as an ordinary couple,

32:37.280 --> 32:39.560
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

32:40.120 --> 32:41.320
shall we?

32:40.330 --> 32:43.630
♫But we're destined to part♫

32:44.300 --> 32:50.170
♫How can I downplay this?♫

32:45.890 --> 32:47.280
Alright.

32:51.290 --> 32:53.960
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

32:54.810 --> 32:57.570
♫When my star falls only for you♫

32:58.440 --> 32:59.970
♫When the heavens fall♫

33:00.610 --> 33:05.470
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

33:06.160 --> 33:08.810
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

33:09.420 --> 33:13.390
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

33:13.940 --> 33:20.890
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

33:18.020 --> 33:19.280
Don't give up.

33:20.460 --> 33:21.990
I have faith in you.

33:21.690 --> 33:24.910
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

33:22.190 --> 33:24.290
You can definitely triumph over Mo Li.

33:26.300 --> 33:28.330
♫When my star falls only for you♫

33:29.590 --> 33:30.600
♫When the heavens fall♫

33:31.520 --> 33:35.960
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

33:37.060 --> 33:39.560
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

33:40.470 --> 33:44.050
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

33:42.490 --> 33:43.620
Xi!

33:44.260 --> 33:45.850
Xi!

33:45.130 --> 33:55.080
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

34:02.380 --> 34:04.560
You keep saying you want to marry Xing Yue,

34:04.580 --> 34:06.420
but that's only because you can't get her

34:06.440 --> 34:08.739
and are trying to claim her through bloodshed.

34:08.760 --> 34:11.540
Love in this world can never come from possession.

34:12.710 --> 34:13.860
Love?

34:15.639 --> 34:16.909
I never needed

34:16.929 --> 34:18.570
such a stupid thing.

34:19.320 --> 34:21.310
I will prove to all of you that

34:22.000 --> 34:23.480
even without love,

34:23.510 --> 34:25.520
I can still have it all.

34:26.530 --> 34:27.880
Xing Yue,

34:28.639 --> 34:31.330
you will be mine.

34:39.370 --> 34:40.810
I finally understand

34:41.920 --> 34:42.960
why ten years ago,

34:42.960 --> 34:45.190
when that demon tried to swallow me and Xi,

34:46.110 --> 34:48.270
he said that Xi had spiritual energy.

34:48.199 --> 34:55.179
[Unbridled Pavilion]

34:48.300 --> 34:49.790
I also finally understand

34:50.000 --> 34:51.880
why Jin Yao couldn't kill her.

34:52.960 --> 34:55.360
Xi was never an ordinary human.

34:55.929 --> 34:57.530
She is the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

34:59.400 --> 35:00.960
I should have guessed it.

35:03.390 --> 35:05.030
The Xing Yue Divine Bow

35:05.050 --> 35:07.020
was born with deity Xing Yue.

35:09.180 --> 35:10.350
Fan Yue.

35:10.700 --> 35:12.740
Don't you think Heaven is so heartless?

35:13.280 --> 35:15.570
Did they bring Xi into this world

35:17.150 --> 35:20.020
just for her to keep sacrificing herself for me?

35:20.890 --> 35:22.100
In this lifetime,

35:22.890 --> 35:24.850
you are Bai Shuo and she is Bai Xi.

35:25.410 --> 35:26.480
You've already surpassed

35:26.480 --> 35:28.060
the relationship between a Supreme Deity and their divine weapon,

35:28.090 --> 35:30.220
and have become each other's closest family in this world.

35:30.650 --> 35:31.570
She saved you

35:32.360 --> 35:34.390
not out of her mission as the Divine Bow,

35:34.660 --> 35:36.370
but as a sister protecting her younger sister.

35:36.920 --> 35:38.580
Her biggest wish

35:38.970 --> 35:40.450
was for you to be well.

35:41.660 --> 35:42.780
For her,

35:44.170 --> 35:45.810
you have to pull yourself together.

35:46.230 --> 35:51.390
[Unbridled Pavilion]

35:46.920 --> 35:48.810
Xi sacrificed her life

35:48.840 --> 35:50.360
in exchange for mine.

35:51.470 --> 35:52.870
I will honor her wish

35:54.010 --> 35:55.480
and be invincible.

35:56.660 --> 35:58.640
I will surely get rid of Mo Li,

35:59.810 --> 36:00.730
avenging her

36:02.700 --> 36:04.700
and all those who have died.

36:09.430 --> 36:10.270
Fan Yue!

36:11.280 --> 36:11.800
Fan Yue!

36:11.820 --> 36:12.510
Master!

36:20.070 --> 36:21.300
What happened?

36:22.610 --> 36:23.630
Master used the Purple Lunar Power

36:23.660 --> 36:25.070
to protect the entire Polar Region.

36:25.090 --> 36:26.960
It has been consuming his divine power,

36:26.980 --> 36:28.850
but with the addition of Mo Li's mass human blood sacrifice,

36:29.140 --> 36:30.330
I'm afraid...

36:30.350 --> 36:31.440
What will happen?

36:31.470 --> 36:33.800
The Purple Moon is extremely yang, while human blood is extremely yin.

36:33.820 --> 36:35.300
With Mo Li's sinister blood sacrifice,

36:35.330 --> 36:37.520
human blood is now infused into the Purple Moon's divine power,

36:37.540 --> 36:38.750
creating a force of both extreme yin and yang

36:38.780 --> 36:40.400
that is clashing in Master's body.

36:40.420 --> 36:41.590
Even with Master's divine body,

36:41.590 --> 36:43.770
he's unable to bear the strain of these two opposing forces.

36:43.800 --> 36:45.260
If this continues,

36:45.540 --> 36:46.910
I'm afraid that Master...

36:47.290 --> 36:49.180
I'm afraid Master's divine vein will snap,

36:49.260 --> 36:51.060
and he will blow up and die.

36:56.420 --> 36:57.610
Stay still!

36:58.130 --> 37:00.300
Mo Li used the Heavenly Divine Miror

37:00.400 --> 37:03.360
to absorb the power of Eternals and demons to practice evil techniques.

37:03.630 --> 37:06.490
His Hidden power is stronger than before.

37:06.830 --> 37:08.160
Stop struggling.

37:08.420 --> 37:10.230
The power of you Eternals and demons

37:10.260 --> 37:13.170
are no match for an ancient deity's divine power.

37:27.230 --> 37:28.650
Mo Li.

37:28.830 --> 37:30.720
Don't you dare assume we'll yield to you

37:30.750 --> 37:32.420
just because you're stronger.

37:33.070 --> 37:34.320
Whether a nobody like you surrenders to me

37:34.320 --> 37:36.100
is of no importance to me.

37:36.120 --> 37:38.350
Either way, I could crush you easily with a flick of my hand.

37:38.380 --> 37:40.380
Why are you gathering all the Eternals and demons together here?

37:40.400 --> 37:42.030
What are you trying to do?

37:42.290 --> 37:45.120
I just want to play a game with all of you.

37:45.450 --> 37:46.410
Bai Shuo.

37:47.060 --> 37:48.770
You guys are familiar with her, right?

37:50.720 --> 37:52.750
Now, all of your lives

37:52.770 --> 37:54.160
are in Bai Shuo’s hands.

37:54.640 --> 37:55.610
Whether you live

37:55.810 --> 37:57.110
or die

37:57.770 --> 37:59.870
is completely up to her.

38:22.990 --> 38:27.940
[To the esteemed Lady Tian Huo]

38:24.040 --> 38:27.040
Hidden Lord Mo Li, with the lives of all Eternals and demons at stake,

38:27.070 --> 38:29.760
demands that Bai Shuo goes to Cold Spring Palace alone

38:29.780 --> 38:31.350
within the next day.

38:31.430 --> 38:34.200
If she does not arrive within the next day, or more than one person arrives,

38:34.220 --> 38:36.380
he will kill all Eternals and demons.

38:36.460 --> 38:38.500
We urge Lady Tian Huo to think carefully.

38:39.210 --> 38:40.880
I've fed him the pill,

38:40.900 --> 38:41.930
but he's still unconscious.

38:44.910 --> 38:45.730
What's wrong?

38:46.110 --> 38:46.900
Nothing.

38:48.040 --> 38:49.040
Tian Huo.

38:49.060 --> 38:50.720
At this point,

38:50.750 --> 38:52.180
no matter what happens,

38:52.210 --> 38:53.290
don't hide anything from me.

38:54.660 --> 38:56.260
It's a letter from the demon warriors.

38:56.280 --> 38:58.120
Mo Li has taken control of all the Eternals and demons

38:58.150 --> 38:59.150
and sent word that

38:59.740 --> 39:01.700
you are to go to Cold Spring Palace alone.

39:01.720 --> 39:03.350
Otherwise, in one day,

39:03.380 --> 39:05.110
he will kill all Eternals and demons.

39:26.620 --> 39:28.860
You were always by my side during

39:29.680 --> 39:31.510
every life-and-death moment in the past.

39:31.880 --> 39:33.090
This time,

39:33.920 --> 39:35.460
I'll have to face it myself.

39:36.610 --> 39:38.590
Do you remember I once said that

39:39.020 --> 39:40.790
the words "Xing Yue's Divine Mantle"

39:41.980 --> 39:43.420
seems very light?

39:45.100 --> 39:47.930
It seems so light that I could just assume it as a story,

39:48.290 --> 39:49.730
but it also seems so heavy.

39:50.920 --> 39:53.400
It's as though the fate of the entire world is weighing down on it.

39:54.720 --> 39:56.230
I'm just a human.

39:56.850 --> 39:59.640
I've never once thought of becoming a deity that could save the world.

40:00.100 --> 40:02.140
But now, the world stands on the brink of catastrophe,

40:02.200 --> 40:04.480
its safety suddenly hanging by a thread.

40:05.160 --> 40:06.750
I cannot,

40:07.550 --> 40:08.870
and will not run away.

40:11.840 --> 40:13.130
Fan Yue.

40:14.760 --> 40:16.610
Forgive me for leaving alone.

40:25.730 --> 40:27.110
Have you really thought it through?

40:27.720 --> 40:29.060
At this point,

40:29.270 --> 40:30.610
I have no choice.

40:30.630 --> 40:32.150
Fan Yue has almost expended himself

40:32.180 --> 40:33.610
just to protect the Eternals and demons.

40:33.890 --> 40:35.800
I won't back down either.

40:35.900 --> 40:37.660
I have no idea if Fan Yue will ever wake up,

40:37.690 --> 40:38.690
or when that might be.

40:39.220 --> 40:41.010
But if he wakes up,

40:41.030 --> 40:42.940
you mustn't let him go to Cold Spring Palace.

40:44.740 --> 40:46.100
You may want to save the Eternals and demons,

40:46.120 --> 40:47.800
but have you ever thought about yourself?

40:48.360 --> 40:49.850
Mo Li is clearly targeting you

40:49.870 --> 40:51.270
by demanding you go alone.

40:55.190 --> 40:57.460
Back when my father was forced to die in Ning'an City,

40:57.900 --> 40:59.380
I hated the world

40:59.410 --> 41:01.490
when I was leaving.

41:01.510 --> 41:02.920
I didn't believe in Eternals,

41:02.940 --> 41:04.790
demons, humans,

41:04.820 --> 41:06.450
and even deities.

41:06.570 --> 41:08.400
But along the way,

41:08.440 --> 41:10.000
I found that among all races,

41:10.030 --> 41:11.800
there are still kindness.

41:11.830 --> 41:13.180
There are countless beings

41:13.200 --> 41:15.500
steadfastly upholding justice and their purpose.

41:15.610 --> 41:17.690
They shouldn't be destroyed this way,

41:17.710 --> 41:19.830
nor should the world end this way.

41:20.120 --> 41:21.960
But the Outlander King's Sword is already broken.

41:22.180 --> 41:23.740
Even if you have the Divine Bow,

41:23.760 --> 41:25.350
you don't have usable arrows.

41:25.370 --> 41:27.280
With just this trace of spiritual power left in you,

41:27.300 --> 41:28.620
your journey

41:29.390 --> 41:31.250
could very easily end in death.

41:31.410 --> 41:32.850
In this world,

41:32.880 --> 41:34.740
it's not always about being certain of success

41:34.760 --> 41:36.830
or guaranteeing that nothing will go wrong before we take action.

41:36.860 --> 41:38.930
Many times, we may not have the upper hand

41:38.950 --> 41:40.590
or any certainty of success,

41:40.610 --> 41:41.860
but we still risk it all

41:41.890 --> 41:43.480
to protect

41:43.510 --> 41:44.940
what matters to us,

41:44.990 --> 41:46.240
don't we?

41:47.040 --> 41:49.770
Everyone has their own responsibilities to fulfil.

41:49.790 --> 41:51.710
Though the physical form of deity Xing Yue may have perished,

41:51.740 --> 41:53.300
its Divine Mantle remains undiminished.

41:53.860 --> 41:56.180
Perhaps, it's also for this very purpose.

41:57.040 --> 41:57.870
Bai Shuo.

41:57.900 --> 41:58.630
Tian Huo.

41:59.740 --> 42:01.290
You've never feared death,

42:01.320 --> 42:02.690
whether it was for Fan Yue

42:02.710 --> 42:04.570
or Bright Moon Palace.

42:04.600 --> 42:06.920
You definitely would know

42:07.110 --> 42:09.110
and understand this feeling.

42:09.140 --> 42:09.970
Right?

42:12.990 --> 42:14.200
Don't worry.

42:14.220 --> 42:15.490
I cherish my life,

42:16.420 --> 42:18.740
and I generally have good luck.

42:18.880 --> 42:20.440
I won't die so easily.

42:35.510 --> 42:36.390
Tian Huo.

42:37.480 --> 42:39.230
It has been my honor

42:39.320 --> 42:40.980
to have known you

42:41.220 --> 42:42.630
and journeyed with you.

42:43.350 --> 42:44.760
Thank you

42:44.780 --> 42:46.130
for everything along the way.

42:46.990 --> 42:48.640
If I ever make it back,

42:49.090 --> 42:50.400
let's have a drink together.

43:04.580 --> 43:05.850
Bai Shuo is here.

43:06.900 --> 43:08.250
She really came.

43:10.200 --> 43:12.170
I didn't expect her to come.

43:22.770 --> 43:24.250
You really came.

43:25.240 --> 43:26.360
What?

43:26.440 --> 43:28.320
Did Fan Yue not stop you?

43:28.350 --> 43:30.680
Or is he simply too weak to stop you?

43:30.970 --> 43:32.060
Let them go.

43:34.200 --> 43:37.280
Both the Eternals and demons have never been nice to you.

43:37.320 --> 43:38.650
They either look down on you

43:38.670 --> 43:40.190
or have been itching to fight or kill you.

43:40.220 --> 43:41.490
And yet, you still want to save them?

43:42.440 --> 43:44.400
There's no need for all this nonsense.

43:44.920 --> 43:46.520
You set the terms,

43:46.540 --> 43:48.180
and I showed up as agreed.

43:48.200 --> 43:49.560
I have done what I needed to do.

43:50.070 --> 43:51.710
You should keep your promise too.

43:51.740 --> 43:52.700
Fine.

43:53.120 --> 43:55.430
As long as you promise me one thing,

43:55.450 --> 43:58.070
I will spare all of them.

43:58.140 --> 43:59.180
Bai Shuo.

43:59.300 --> 44:00.530
Don't believe him.

44:00.550 --> 44:01.650
Mo Li is ruthless.

44:01.680 --> 44:03.370
He won't give up so easily.

44:04.970 --> 44:06.030
How noisy.

44:09.820 --> 44:10.720
Where did they go?

44:10.740 --> 44:11.680
Don't worry.

44:11.700 --> 44:13.340
They went back to where they came from.

44:13.370 --> 44:15.210
Their lives are mine

44:15.230 --> 44:17.090
to take at any moment, anyway.

44:17.120 --> 44:18.680
What do you want me to do?

44:18.700 --> 44:20.960
The wedding that was left unfinished 60,000 years ago

44:21.960 --> 44:24.070
should now be completed.

44:24.220 --> 44:25.920
I'm not Xing Yue.

44:25.940 --> 44:26.860
It doesn't matter.

44:27.460 --> 44:28.710
I just want to finish

44:28.730 --> 44:30.820
what I didn't finish 60,000 years ago.

44:30.940 --> 44:33.120
So regardless whether you are Xing Yue or not,

44:33.150 --> 44:34.470
simply just with your face,

44:34.490 --> 44:36.340
I must marry you.
